the open-source license of the client library.

Bundled FFmpeg notice

VoiceBridge uses FFmpeg by launching bundled executables/runtime media components
as separate tools. The bundled Windows ffmpeg.exe currently comes from Gyan.dev
and identifies itself as GPLv3 because it is built with GPL/version3 options.
When redistributing binaries, keep FFmpeg notices, license terms and source-code
availability obligations separate and visible alongside the VoiceBridge bundle.
